resources.string: KC Restaurant in Delhi. Chinese Restaurants with Address, Contact Number, Photos, Maps. View KC Restaurant, Delhi on Justdial. Making way for a hearty meal is KC Restaurant in Delhi. Established in the year 2014, this place is synonymous with delicious food that can satiate all food cravings. It is home to some of the most appreciated cuisines which include Chinese. So as to be able to cater to a large number of diners, it occupies a favourable location at Dwarka Sector 7.
Address: C-396, Dwarka Sector 7, Delhi - 110075, Near Ramphal Chowk, Opposite Relaxo Showroom, Palam Extension
